能<br />\n<br />\n聖女讚歌：<br />\n主要拎喵幣同角色碎片，每日唔同角色，分幾種難度但只影響每場拎到幾多喵幣(簡單1個普通3個etc)<br />\n完成3場後就拎到獎勵(固定10喵幣3碎片1轉強券1時裝券)<br />\n如果喵幣商店無乜特別想買，打3場簡單拎3+10喵幣收工<br />\n<br />\n清完呢d基本野就睇你刷裝備 刷材料衝rank 刷收集品 定刷羈絆拎碎片 又或者去挑戰彈幕 又或者釣魚掛機(一開始唔建議玩煮野食，食材太貴)<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想買體力就探索30分鐘有機會拎12體<br />\n又或者探索2小時有機會拎30體<br />\n<br />\n*探險神社係拎異世界通行證，打塔時係指定層數farm材料用，拎唔拎隨你"},{"pid":"9c681a80892a99e8f0ce4d5259b7bcb6f979b4f5","tid":986493,"uid":56057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"有無會收人"},{"pid":"65bfa1722ad770dffa6ff9799c88879441612207","tid":986493,"uid":117082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c681a80892a99e8f0ce4d5259b7bcb6f979b4f5","tid":986493,"uid":56057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"有無會收人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:04:12.000Z","msg":"未成年少女， 巴哈有post招人"},{"pid":"ee98deac7770a9e00ce42c999b9d45b696233127","tid":986493,"uid":56057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65bfa1722ad770dffa6ff9799c88879441612207","tid":986493,"uid":117082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c681a80892a99e8f0ce4d5259b7bcb6f979b4f5","tid":986493,"uid":56057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"有無會收人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:04:12.000Z","msg":"未成年少女， 巴哈有post招人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"爆人"},{"pid":"badab0887e4c5a349ffa3ad8709c09de1cd4386c","tid":986493,"uid":146690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"都係咁少人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f1df3bf4a518745c0511d52562b76d76000248","tid":986493,"uid":146690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"我成功引誘多左身邊兩個朋友玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cb01b96df22794cf0